  "about_the_game": "This is an exciting and interesting action adventure game. You can control monsters to fight. The game includes single-person adventure, single-person Roguelike, or 2-person duel, 5-person team adventure, 5V5 camp battle, and 20-person chaos fight!<br><br>The game is a overlooking angle battle. There will be many props in the battle. After you pass the pass, you can use the enemy defeated at this pass to fight. You need to be careful of all kinds of mechanisms in the scene!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >single mode</h2>Difficult and refreshing combat experience<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/d60bd8e4aceaedd214be5cb20936d410.poster.avif?t=1768816351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/d60bd8e4aceaedd214be5cb20936d410.webm?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/d60bd8e4aceaedd214be5cb20936d410.mp4?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >team play</h2>Intense and exciting cooperative battle<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/cb19fc84e15a9d81a2160627c69e2485.poster.avif?t=1768816351\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/cb19fc84e15a9d81a2160627c69e2485.webm?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139890/extras/cb19fc84e15a9d81a2160627c69e2485.mp4?t=1768816351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Battle</h2>4 online playing methods, waiting for you to experience<br><